t generally popular until the 19th century, when many medieval names were revived. It has now fallen from favour again."],"variants":[]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Attainment’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Gertrude de Falvy was born in 1280, in Falvy, Somme, Hauts-de-France, France, her father, Ecuyer Pierre I de Quincy et de Montauban, was 25 and her mother, Marie de Bazentin, was 25. She married Baudouin I de Renty in 1299, in Falvy, Somme, Hauts-de-France, France. They were the parents of at least 5 sons and 2 daughters. She died in Renty, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France."},"et":{"1280–":"1280–Surnud","1280–Female":"1280–Surnud","1280–1333":"1280–1333","1300–1369":"1300–1369","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1308–1360":"1308–1360","1312–Male":"1312–Surnud","1316–Female":"1316–Surnud","1320–Male":"1320–Surnud","1322–1379":"1322–1379","1255–Male":"1255–Surnud","1255–Female":"1255–Surnud","Abt 1312":"umbes 1312","1360":"1360","1280":"1280","Abt 1316":"umbes 1316","1316":"1316","1369":"1369","1379":"1379","Abt 1300":"umbes 1300","1312":"1312","1300":"1300","1322":"1322","1333":"1333","1299":"1299","Abt 1320":"umbes 1320","1255":"1255","1320":"1320","1308":"1308","Renty, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Frankrijk":"Renty, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa","Renty, Saint-Omer, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France":"Renty, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa","Falvy, Somme, Hauts-de-France, France":"Falvy, Somme, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1280–":"1280–Kuollut","1280–Female":"1280–Kuollut","1280–1333":"1280–1333","1300–1369":"1300–1369","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1308–1360":"1308–1360","1312–Male":"1312–Kuollut","1316–Female":"1316–Kuollut","1320–Male":"1320–Kuollut","1322–1379":"1322–1379","1255–Male":"1255–Kuollut","1255–Female":"1255–Kuollut","Abt 1312":"noin 1312","1360":"1360","1280":"1280","Abt 1316":"noin 1316","131